    "The process covers preparation, material handling, distribution, approval, and post-meeting follow-up.",
    "All materials must be submitted to the Chief Legal Officer (CLO) and CFO for review within 48 hours of receipt.",
    "Once approved, the CFO authorizes the Corporate Paralegal to upload materials into Nasdaq Boardvantage (NBV).",
    "Materials are attached to the corresponding NBV meeting.",
